  "title": "Killed to Death",
  "description": "This quirky murder-mystery is a love letter to the genre. Inspired by \"Death by Design\" by Rob Urbinati with tributes to \"Clue\" and \"Murder by Death\" this rollercoaster ride incorporates a new twist, what if a traditional murder-mystery...was also a soap opera!?",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Megan Holt<br><strong>Director</strong>: Megan Holt<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Tyler Herzberg, Christina Holt, Grace Jenkins, Spenser Kells, Alexandra Lepage, Jack Walker<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Christina Holt<br/></br>",
  "website": "https://www.instagram.com/suttontheatrecompany",
  "plain_language": "Killed to Death follows a dramatic Hollywood couple. Their soap opera and relationship are both falling apart. To escape the critics, they flee to their country home. When a few unexpected guests arrive, things get more complicated and someone ends up dead! The quirky group must uncover old secrets to catch the killer before they strike again.",
